[[[picture ensureFacesStorage.picture addFace: (faceWithPicture := face copy).faceWithPicture.]]]%So  me interesting reading about *The First Notebook War>https://yihui.name/en/2018/09/notebook-war/* ! AuthoringLet's create now have a look how to create a document from scratch in a new file ${inputFile:path=demo.pillar}$..! Download*Glamorous Toolkit>http://gtoolkit.com*

